---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const siblingServices = [
  { name: "Relaxation Dentistry for Nervous Patients", href: "/services/ivs/relaxation" },
  { name: "Sedation Options for Sensitive Teeth or Gag Reflex", href: "/services/ivs/sensitive-teeth", current: true },
  { name: "Stress-Free Dental Visits with IV Sedation", href: "/services/ivs/stress-free" },
  { name: "Monitoring and Safe Sedation Care", href: "/services/ivs/monitoring" },
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Sedation for Sensitive Teeth Lethbridge | Able Family Dental"
  description="IV sedation for patients with sensitive teeth or a strong gag reflex in Lethbridge. Dr. Tyler Snow provides safe, comfortable sedation dentistry. Call 403.327.7202."
>

  <!-- ============================================================
       HERO
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[42%] pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
      <img
        src="/images/services/hero-iv-sensitive-teeth.jpg"
        alt=""
        width="800"
        height="600"
        loading="eager"
        decoding="async"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 w-2/5" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-brand-primary), transparent);"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-wide relative py-16 lg:py-24 lg:max-w-[64%]">
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)] mb-5" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/" class="text-white hover:text-white/80 transition-colors">Home</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <a href="/services/" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-colors">Services</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <a href="/services/ivs/" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-colors">IV Sedation</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <span class="text-white">Sensitive Teeth &amp; Gag Reflex</span>
      </nav>
      <p class="eyebrow text-white">IV Sedation Dentistry</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-5xl)] leading-tight text-white max-w-2xl">
        Sedation Options for Sensitive Teeth or Gag Reflex
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)] leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
        Heightened tooth sensitivity and a strong gag reflex can make even routine dental visits uncomfortable. IV sedation provides effective relief, allowing care to proceed without distress or interruption.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       MAIN CONTENT + SIDEBAR
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="section-y bg-white">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_300px] gap-12">

        <!-- LEFT: Main content -->
        <div class="space-y-10">

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-3xl)] text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-4">
              When sensitivity or gag reflex gets in the way
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-text)] leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                Dental sensitivity and gag reflex are among the most common reasons patients find dental care difficult or even impossible to complete. These are not personal failings, they are physiological responses that vary significantly from person to person, and they can make otherwise straightforward procedures genuinely challenging.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong class="text-[var(--color-brand-primary)]">Tooth sensitivity</strong> can make it uncomfortable to have instruments near the teeth or gumline, even with local anaesthetic in place. For some patients, sensitivity is localised; for others, it affects most or all of the mouth.
              </p>
              <p>
                A <strong class="text-[var(--color-brand-primary)]">sensitive gag reflex</strong> can be triggered by dental instruments, impression materials, x-ray sensors, or simply having the mouth held open for a period of time. In some cases, it can make it nearly impossible to complete routine procedures without significant discomfort.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-3xl)] text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-4">
              How IV sedation helps
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-text)] leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                IV sedation suppresses the gag reflex significantly, allowing procedures that would otherwise be stopped short to be completed comfortably and efficiently. Patients who have had difficulty with impressions, x-rays, or longer procedures often find that IV sedation makes these entirely manageable.
              </p>
              <p>
                For patients with sensitivity, the deeply relaxed state produced by IV sedation reduces the physical response to stimuli that would otherwise cause discomfort. Combined with local anaesthetic where needed, IV sedation allows comprehensive treatment to proceed without the involuntary reactions that interrupted care in the past.
              </p>
              <p>
                Dr. Tyler Snow's certification in moderate conscious IV sedation means the level of sedation can be carefully adjusted to your needs, deep enough to be effective, while keeping you safe and responsive throughout.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-3xl)] text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-4">
              Common procedures where sedation helps
            </h2>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              {[
                { label: "Dental impressions and x-rays", note: "Tray-based impressions and intraoral sensors can trigger gag reflex; sedation allows these to be completed without interruption." },
                { label: "Deep cleanings and scaling", note: "Patients with sensitivity in the gumline area often find these procedures more comfortable under sedation." },
                { label: "Extractions and oral surgery", note: "Sedation reduces stress on the patient and allows the dentist to work efficiently, particularly for more involved procedures." },
                { label: "Restorative work", note: "Fillings, crowns, and other treatments that require working throughout the mouth benefit from the reduced sensitivity and gag suppression sedation provides." },
                { label: "Multiple procedures in one visit", note: "Sedation allows more to be accomplished in a single appointment, reducing the total number of visits for patients who find dental care difficult." },
              ].map(item => (
                <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-accent)] shrink-0 mt-2" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] text-sm">{item.label}</p>
                    <p class="mt-0.5 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">{item.note}</p>
                  </div>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Callout -->
          <div class="bg-[var(--color-surface-cool)] rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[var(--color-border-soft)]">
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-accent)] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-base text-[var(--color-brand-primary)]">A suitability assessment comes first</h3>
                <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
                  IV sedation is appropriate for most healthy adults, but we review your medical history and current medications before proceeding. If you have questions about whether sedation is right for you, call our office and we will be happy to discuss it before booking.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT: Sidebar -->
        <aside class="space-y-6">

          <!-- Book CTA card -->
          <div class="bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] rounded-2xl p-6 text-white">
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-white">Ready to Book?</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)]">Call us or request an appointment online, new patients welcome.</p>
            <a href="/book/" class="mt-4 btn btn-primary w-full block text-center">Book Appointment</a>
            <a href="/refer/" class="mt-2 btn btn-outline w-full block text-center">Refer Patient</a>
            <a href="tel:+14033277202" class="mt-2 block text-center text-sm text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)] hover:text-white transition-colors">403.327.7202</a>
          </div>

          <!-- Sibling services card -->
          <div class="bg-[var(--color-surface-cool)] rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[var(--color-border-soft)]">
            <h3 class="font-body text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-4">IV Sedation Services</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              {siblingServices.map(svc => (
                <li>
                  {svc.current ? (
                    <span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-brand-accent)]">
                      <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-accent)] shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                      {svc.name}
                    </span>
                  ) : (
                    <a href={svc.href} class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] transition-colors">
                      <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-border-soft)] shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                      {svc.name}
                    </a>
                  )}
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>

        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       CTA BAND
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] py-16 text-center overflow-hidden relative">
    <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-none" viewBox="0 0 1440 160" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M0 60 C 240 20, 480 100, 720 60 C 960 20, 1200 100, 1440 60 L1440 160 L0 160 Z" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.03)"/>
    </svg>
    <div class="relative container-wide">
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-4xl)] text-white leading-tight">Ready to book?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)] text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">Call <a href="tel:+14033277202" class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-[var(--color-brand-accent-soft)] transition-colors">403.327.7202</a> or request an appointment online.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/book/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Book Appointment</a>
        <a href="/refer/" class="btn btn-lg border border-white/30 text-white hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">Refer Patient</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-lg border border-white/30 text-white hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
